title: Nutrient Breakdown by Processing Class and Store
description: This project illustrates the differences in nutrient content among various food processing classses and retail stores.

title: Clash Royale Card Synergies and Deck Compositions
description: Uses meta-clustering with K-Means and Gaussian Mixture Models to identify card synergies for optimal deck building in Clash Royale.

title: Recipies Explored
description: An exploration of recipes from a food.com dataset, analyzing ingredients, cooking times, and nutrition to recommend recipies to users.
